			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Update to this quest. Tinkerers at www.tinkering.org have found out that the gemcutter (a tinkered item) can be used in place of the Darfumpel part of this quest.<BR>
<BR>
Take one gemcutter and one uncut hyacinth and put into a jewelry bag. Have a high-level jeweler combine these items and you still receive the faceted Hyacinth. <BR>
<BR>
Surely Tinker/Jewelers will be willing to do the cut cheaper than Darfumpel. Find a Tinker/Jeweler and maybe save yourself a few hundred plat off this already expensive quest.<BR>
<BR>
Igbert<BR>
203 Tinker<BR>

