			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just completed this quest today.  Bought all the items in the EC tunnel:  crystalline orb, prickly pear &amp; white gold necklace.  Cost me 1500pp for all 3.  Then gave the 3000pp to the NPCs in Rathe.  Killed the Monstrous Zombie with myself (51sk), a 58 monk, a 55 cleric, a 54 druid, a 51 pally (yes a pally helped me get this SK spell - such irony) and a 50 warrior.  The zombie went down easy for us nobody was ever close to being in danger of death.<BR>
<BR>
And... this spell rules.  Lower cast time than Siphon Life. Long recast (2 min) but you can usually get 2 off per fight.  That does 560dmg to mob and 560 health for you.  a 1120hp swing.  Use siphon life in between (no recast time/nice mana/hp ratio) and it makes the SK class almost overbalanced.  I am still soloing and leveling at 51.<BR>
<BR>
Gallager Melonsmasher<BR>
51 Reaver<BR>
Morell-Thule
